001package com.commercetools.graphql.api.client;
002
003import com.netflix.graphql.dgs.client.codegen.BaseSubProjectionNode;
004
005public class OrderExcerptProjection<PARENT extends BaseSubProjectionNode<?, ?>, ROOT extends BaseSubProjectionNode<?, ?>> extends BaseSubProjectionNode<PARENT, ROOT> {
006  public OrderExcerptProjection(PARENT parent, ROOT root) {
007    super(parent, root, java.util.Optional.of("OrderExcerpt"));
008  }
009
010  public MoneyProjection<OrderExcerptProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> totalPrice() {
011     MoneyProjection<OrderExcerptProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new MoneyProjection<>(this, getRoot());
012     getFields().put("totalPrice", projection);
013     return projection;
014  }
015
016  public TaxedPriceProjection<OrderExcerptProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> taxedPrice() {
017     TaxedPriceProjection<OrderExcerptProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new TaxedPriceProjection<>(this, getRoot());
018     getFields().put("taxedPrice", projection);
019     return projection;
020  }
021
022  public OrderExcerptProjection<PARENT, ROOT> version() {
023    getFields().put("version", null);
024    return this;
025  }
026}
